| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5096 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 00fb7ee6-c2ed-57c1-a18e-901beb4c41f8"
